<LanguageData>
  
  <!-- EN: Crashed MegaCorp Transport -->
  <Wolfein_ShuttleCrashed.label>已坠毁的军企运输机</Wolfein_ShuttleCrashed.label>
  <!-- EN: The wreckage of a heavy transport developed by the Wolfein military MegaCorp. This model was originally designed for the rapid deployment of high-intensity combat units within an atmosphere. After suffering severe damage during the forced landing, the aircraft has completely lost its flight and transport capabilities, leaving behind nothing but a mass of metal wreckage still radiating residual heat. -->
  <Wolfein_ShuttleCrashed.description>一架沃芬族军工军企开发的重型运输机残骸。该型号原本用于在大气层内快速部署高强度战力单位，如今机体在迫降过程中遭受严重损伤，已完全失去飞行与运输功能，只剩下一具仍在散发余热的金属残骸。</Wolfein_ShuttleCrashed.description>
  
